track_notes: Good gravel all the way to the top. See AK7U write up. http://www.pnwsota.org/blog/ak7u/2024-october-23/panther-rock-drive

This route is from Panther Rock to Table Rock trailhead. Note that the road is rough from Panther Rock to the river. We made it down in a Rav4. 4wd pickup or more capable rig would be needed to get from the river to Panther Rock.
track_title: Panther Rock to Table Rock TH
